Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from this way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This wind is out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the group ahead finished up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wind here is different{\i0}\N{\i1}than on the green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's blowing the complete{\i0}\N{\i1}opposite direction now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not just{\i0}\N{\i1}changing directions either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With today's pin position,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you miss the pin\Nto the to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,an uphill approach is left.\NGetting par should be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I give advice on where to\Naim, it won't be easy with this wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even Tonbo will be able to use{\i0}\N{\i1}this wind to her advantage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hard to play the wind when you{\i0}\N{\i1}can't read its direction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only judgement we can make{\i0}\N{\i1}is choosing which club to use.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo has been holding that club{\i0}\N{\i1}for a while now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She knew which one{\i0}\N{\i1}she wanted to use from the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean she's able to read the{\i0}\N{\i1}wind even as it changes this much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wind is playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like golfing on the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The three iron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}150 yards to the pin.{\i0}\N{\i1}Is she reading it as a head wind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never wore a hat when I{\i0}\N{\i1}played on the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} My hair was always{\i0}\N{\i1}blowing like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igaiga is here too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ground is hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is so much fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a swing was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's rolling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's avoiding the wind altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A hole-in-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball ended up \Nin the best spot possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never would have{\i0}\N{\i1}thought to do that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if thought of it,{\i0}\N{\i1}I wouldn't do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like I can't call that cool...{\i0}\N{\i1}Can I even call it real golf?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait... who am I to judge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who am I to decide what real golf is?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice par.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo has par.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her total is still an even par.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She made it through{\i0}\N{\i1}this difficult hole with ease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems like it's blowing{\i0}\N{\i1}mainly to the right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven iron please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take a bet on that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. The wind is blowing to the left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It changed to a head wind. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be the end for all of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo will take the lead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I persevere, I can get ahead{\i0}\N{\i1}of Ema and Hinoki. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can take the lead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To make that happen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A spoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's doing it Tonbo's way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She aimed for the same spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to hold back.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm going to win this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She hits her wedge and putter with{\i0}\N{\i1}her right hand. And she's good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She hits hard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but perhaps her previous play style{\i0}\N{\i1}used delicate techniques.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't afford to\Nlet their guard down for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I'm holding up well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, the seventh hole{\i0}\N{\i1}was the turning point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were all tied until then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the\Nsecond group is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Tonbo's first half went?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few players so far
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,finished the first half\Nwith a score in the thirties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ones that did\Ndid it before this wind picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else was in the forties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she drops\Nfive or six strokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,she's still hitting average.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's hitting her third stroke\Nfrom the fairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right behind the pin.\NShould we move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think\Nshe'll hit it from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She has about a\Nthirty-five yard approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have to\Ndo anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs to focus on distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but that won't be easy\Nwith this wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's a head wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hits too hard and it\Ngoes beyond the pin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,her fourth stroke\Nwill be a downhill putt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That will put the\Nwind behind the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,pushing the ball along strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't go in the cup,\Nthe wind will carry it right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to land it below the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it isn't perfect,\Nshe'll have to leave an uphill putt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igaiga is by my side. Alright.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Right on target!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She often did that on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By hitting a full lob\Nagainst the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the ball falls down\Nand stops dead in its tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo gets a kick out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to scare Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just roll it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No one in their right mind\Nwould lob it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! My first birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Tonbo chip it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A birdie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's tied with Ema and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first birdie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is quite windy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How many bogies did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one under?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So nobody achieved\Na green in regulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for the last group,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,no one is playing\Nvery well in this wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She opened the face up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to lob it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Only Tonbo would\Ntake a risk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to mark it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a fine approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a critical moment. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If my score drops below Tsubura's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no chance of winning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can keep my game up until{\i0}\N{\i1}Tsubura's own score drops{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be able to apply pressure{\i0}\N{\i1}and find my momentum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't lose my nerve!{\i0}\N{\i1}Everything has been going well so far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to finish the first half{\i0}\N{\i1}with my two-stroke lead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a shank!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things are turning in my favor. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be{\i0}\N{\i1}a double-bogey for Tsubura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm enjoying my opponent's mistakes.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm hoping for trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't I stay positive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't I focus on{\i0}\N{\i1}just being the best I can be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No practice swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't like this version of myself.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm know I'm going to pay for being mean.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it, this is my punishment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... maybe it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They said I'm the only one\Nto finish the first half under par!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy, Igaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Believing this is the half way point\Nof the game is too leisurely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In professional golf, it's not\Nhalfway over until the tenth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The final three holes require as much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or even more energy\Nthan the previous fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Igaiga\Nwould be proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo finished the first half\Nunder par!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only one stroke\Nbehind the leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She might actually have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to tell everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei doesn't have a phone.\NWho can I send a message to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Toshima Village City Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hello, the name's Igarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I work at the\NHinoshima Development Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They call me "Igaiga" on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attention. This is the{\i0}\N{\i1}Toshima Village Disaster Center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have an emergency{\i0}\N{\i1}broadcast from a man named Igaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, I have absolutely{\i0}\N{\i1}no idea what he's talking about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While quite out of the ordinary,{\i0}\N{\i1}he told me it's very important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will now share with you exactly{\i0}\N{\i1}what he told me to say:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo has closed the gap{\i0}\N{\i1}to just one stroke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}behind the leader at the end{\i0}\N{\i1}of the front nine on the final day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or... something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei! Did you hear\Nthe announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you call me "honey" or\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo has closed the gap{\i0}\N{\i1}to just one stroke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}behind the leader at the end{\i0}\N{\i1}of the front nine on the final day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so concludes our broadcast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come in\Nthe clubhouse dressed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki!\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I tell him I hit forty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've held your top position\Ndespite this powerful wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no reason\Nto be looking so down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You played wonderfuly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Superintendant Nakase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Hinoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave here at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue to cause trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have to resort\Nto drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Drastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it, but I have\Na strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my golf course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't listen to what I say,\Nyou'll pay the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki has moved onto\Nthe second half in the top position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She has?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only that were the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm able to win,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't win by only one stroke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I had taken a one stroke{\i0}\N{\i1}penalty back then, I could have won.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I have to get two strokes{\i0}\N{\i1}ahead. I have to win by two strokes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see Tonbo on the fairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not out of bounds,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but even if she gets on the fairway,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she'll use her third stroke{\i0}\N{\i1}to get on the green{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll have to make it in one putt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This could hurt her score.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where you hit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to aim low\Nto avoid the branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The widest spot is over here,\Nbut there's a bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The right side of the woods is a{\i0}\N{\i1}depression set back from the fairway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Getting on the fairway will be tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could get a bogey or worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about getting par.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure\Nyou don't get a double bogey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too far to the right!\NEven farther than the green!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to hit it through\Nthat little opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Any farther and \Nit'll go out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It went though!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn, turn, turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the green!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It rolled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need a provisional ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hitting a provisional ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get it right this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hurt yourself \Nany more than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A provisional ball.{\i0}\N{\i1}Next will be her fourth stroke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One to the fairway,{\i0}\N{\i1}then on the green in five.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two putts could give{\i0}\N{\i1}her a double bogey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that happens,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} the all-powerful Tonbo will be{\i0}\N{\i1}dropped from the competition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The bunker is a safe spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still 180 yards. That should\Nbe no problem for y--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're aiming for the green again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're aiming up this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she insane?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:18:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hope for others' failure.{\i0}\N{\i1}Tonbo. That's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting narrower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And wider again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time it sways...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Robin ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Right by the pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She can finish with a bogey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I found my first ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's in a good spot, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She got a par after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It stopped too soon.{\i0}\N{\i1}There's still a long putt left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's totally stuck. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it came down, I'd be able to{\i0}\N{\i1}hit is as my second stroke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try shaking the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If the ball that falls down\Nreally is yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get a penalty stroke\Nfor moving the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to put it back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is your ball, you'll have to\Ndeclare it as unplayable first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Without going closer to the pin, \Nyou can drop it straight down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and within two club lengths\Nof where it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or drop it alone the extended line\Nfrom the spot to the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take your\Nthird short from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I'll be able to\Naim for the green.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's much better\Nthan the other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is my ball,\Nthen I'm calling it unplayable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why won't it come down? If it doesn't{\i0}\N{\i1}come down I won't be able to win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your ball stuck, Hinoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure\Nit really is my ball first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a Callaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one! It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got a putt left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She came all the way\Nhere to find your ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo is always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when we were{\i0}\N{\i1}practicing on the course,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she ran all over{\i0}\N{\i1}looking for lost balls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And look at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've even messed with the score just to{\i0}\N{\i1}win ahead of Tonbo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this really who{\i0}\N{\i1}you want to be, Hinoki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too out of breath to putt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Tonbo miss the par putt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Her first bogey?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She came to find my ball.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She did it for me. I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved my ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever felt pressured before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always suffering from it during matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really feeling it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:23:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,First Time Under Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got pressure in my tummy\Nfrom all that breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called eating too much.
